!!!
%html{ lang: 'ja' }
  %head
    %meta{ charset: 'utf-8' }
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0", :name => "viewport"}
      %title= content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title) : "Mongr"
      %meta{:content => content_for?(:description) ? yield(:description) : "Mongr", :name => "description"}
        = stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all"
        -# = stylesheet_link_tag "//yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.2.0/pure-min.css", :media => "all"
        = javascript_include_tag "application"
        = csrf_meta_tags
        = yield(:head)
  %body{:class => "#{controller_name} #{action_name}"}
    .pure-g-r#layout
      .pure-u#nav
        .nav-inner
          .profile
            .pure-g
              .pure-u
                = image_tag 'http://si0.twimg.com/profile_images/2672327531/a0f29b6c75ed6067c3daffee2bbdd72d.png'
              .pure-u-2-3
                .profile-nickname
                  %span supermomonga
          .pure-menu.pure-menu-open
            %ul
              %li.pure-menu-heading Rooms
              %li.active= link_to 'じょうほうかがく！', '/'
              %li= link_to raw('vim-users.jp <span class="room-count">(2)</span>'), '/'
              %li= link_to 'Emasc', '/'
              %li= link_to 'SandBox', '/'
              %li= link_to 'Ruby', '/'
              %li= link_to 'Go言語', '/'
              %li= link_to 'Qt Users', '/'
      .pure-u#main
        .content
          .chat-content-header.pure-g
            .pure-u-1-3
              %h1 じょうほうかがく！
            .chat-content-header-controls.pure-u-2-3
              %button.pure-button.secondary-button Members(12)
              %button.pure-button.secondary-button Bots(192)
              %button.pure-button.secondary-button Detail
              %button.pure-button.secondary-button Search
              %button.pure-button.secondary-button Archive
          .chat-content-items
            .pure-g.chat-item
              .pure-u.chat-avatar= image_tag 'http://si0.twimg.com/profile_images/3484982396/ce2d081bb91c93151b61f6e784069cf6.jpeg'
              .pure-u
                %h5.chat-name mopp
                %p.chat-message
                  やばみ
            .pure-g.chat-item
              .pure-u.chat-avatar= image_tag 'http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/d9d0ceb387e3b6de5c4562af78e8a910.jpg?s=64'
              .pure-u
                %h5.chat-name ujihisa
                %p.chat-message
                  こんな風にsleepいれたけど再現できないなあ
            .pure-g.chat-item
              .pure-u.chat-avatar= image_tag 'http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/3b83f8f7a25019f3ee01791df024bf3c.jpg?s=64'
              .pure-u
                %h5.chat-name thinca
                %p.chat-message
                  あれ、そう言えばujihisaさん、昨日の分の VAC は?
            .pure-g.chat-item.notification-item
              .pure-u
                %p.notification-message
                  supermomonga is now online
            - 20.times do
              .pure-g.chat-item
                .pure-u.chat-avatar= image_tag 'http://si0.twimg.com/profile_images/2672327531/a0f29b6c75ed6067c3daffee2bbdd72d.png'
                .pure-u
                  %h5.chat-name supermomonga
                  %p.chat-message
                    hi
          .chat-content-input
            %form.pure-form.pure-form-stacked
              %textarea.pure-input-1

